{"name":"Approve requests with Discord and Google Drive hands-free","nodes":[{"parameters":{"formTitle":"Approve requests with Discord and Google Drive hands-free","formFields":{"values":[{"fieldLabel":"Title","requiredField":true},{"fieldLabel":"Assignee","requiredField":false},{"fieldLabel":"Duedate","requiredField":false}]},"options":{"appendAttribution":false}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.formTrigger","typeVersion":2.2,"position":[-270,400],"id":"4cc040cc-5aad-417b-9caf-a60119f766dd","name":"New Task Form Submission","webhookId":"396d4da1-89b0-4627-9433-743a2982cb6e"},{"parameters":{"rules":{"values":[{"conditions":{"options":{"caseSensitive":true,"leftValue":"","typeValidation":"strict","version":2},"conditions":[{"id":"a22b0fa4-3b6f-48d8-ba48-35e005473592","leftValue":"={{ $json.kind || $json.type || 'standard' }}","rightValue":"auto-approve","operator":{"type":"string","operation":"equals"}}],"combinator":"and"},"renameOutput":true,"outputKey":"auto-approve"},{"conditions":{"options":{"caseSensitive":true,"leftValue":"","typeValidation":"strict","version":2},"conditions":[{"id":"f1531f63-ebfe-4649-8632-f8a02518b8f3","leftValue":"={{ $json.kind || $json.type || 'standard' }}","rightValue":"needs-review","operator":{"type":"string","operation":"equals"}}],"combinator":"and"},"renameOutput":true,"outputKey":"needs-review"}]},"options":{"fallbackOutput":"extra"}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.switch","typeVersion":3.2,"position":[54,400],"id":"af46d82f-1098-4f80-b981-73d9a2f4e86c","name":"Route by Work Type"},{"parameters":{"operation":"appendOrUpdate","documentId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"","cachedResultName":"Task Tracker"},"sheetName":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"Main","cachedResultName":"Main"},"columns":{"mappingMode":"autoMapInputData","value":{},"matchingColumns":["taskId"],"schema":[]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.googleSheets","typeVersion":4.7,"position":[378,130],"id":"44575ab6-9df8-43a0-a691-520da23bfd95","name":"Process 'auto-approve' → Google Sheets","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"authentication":"webhook","content":"=🚀 Priority task handled: {{ $json.taskId }}","options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.discord","typeVersion":2,"position":[702,640],"id":"962dd1b3-683a-4a62-9076-cd8d339c48f4","name":"Fast-Track 'needs-review' + Alert","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"operation":"append","documentId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"","cachedResultName":"Task Tracker"},"sheetName":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"Main","cachedResultName":"Main"},"columns":{"mappingMode":"autoMapInputData","value":{},"matchingColumns":[],"schema":[]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.googleSheets","typeVersion":4.7,"position":[1026,1150],"id":"2d825daa-d039-486d-aaa4-da3092a90858","name":"Hold Unknown Types (DLQ)","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"mode":"append","numberInputs":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.merge","typeVersion":3.2,"position":[1674,400],"id":"ce37b436-572b-48e5-824c-cc8afb3b21dc","name":"Merge Routed Work"},{"parameters":{"operation":"getCurrentDate","outputFieldName":"processedAt","options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.dateTime","typeVersion":2,"position":[2646,400],"id":"2d9cd2bd-3922-4654-8534-5de9268e9c55","name":"Stamp Processing Time"},{"parameters":{"keys":{"key":[{"currentKey":"id","newKey":"taskId"}]},"additionalOptions":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.renameKeys","typeVersion":1,"position":[2970,400],"id":"c744b59b-147b-488f-9035-875f80e89b44","name":"Align Field Names"},{"parameters":{"maxItems":100},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.limit","typeVersion":1,"position":[3294,400],"id":"4415682a-52fa-40a9-9ddd-4a26b170841d","name":"Cap Batch Volume"},{"parameters":{"content":"### New Task Form Submission\n\nServes an n8n-hosted form (Title, Assignee, Duedate). Each submission becomes one execution.\n\nNext: Route by Work Type","width":280,"height":232,"color":5},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-330,520],"id":"fb87af04-bc58-3ea2-c14c-6744c71ae543","name":"Note: New Task Form Submission"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Route by Work Type\n\nRoutes each item to one of 3 lanes: auto-approve, needs-review + fallback.\n\nPorts: ①→ Process 'auto-approve' → Google Sheets · ②→ Fast-Track 'needs-review' + Alert · ③→ Hold Unknown Types (DLQ)","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,520],"id":"0e9878fa-2e21-2891-f0e7-734c7741119a","name":"Note: Route by Work Type"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Process 'auto-approve' → Google Sheets\n\ngoogleSheets — `appendOrUpdate` operation against the connected account.\n\nNext: Merge Routed Work\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,250],"id":"c10725b2-7992-90e0-8009-25b23f89ce0d","name":"Note: Process 'auto-approve' → Google Sheets"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Fast-Track 'needs-review' + Alert\n\ndiscord — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nNext: Merge Routed Work\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Discord webhook URL","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[642,760],"id":"3abd6d61-9e81-5a91-6220-5498d59cee38","name":"Note: Fast-Track 'needs-review' + Alert"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Hold Unknown Types (DLQ)\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nNext: Merge Routed Work\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[966,1270],"id":"5067b3ca-d37c-aa4d-1b37-0d2ec388d06e","name":"Note: Hold Unknown Types (DLQ)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Merge Routed Work\n\nRejoins 3 branches into one stream (mode: append) so downstream logic runs once.\n\nNext: Stamp Processing Time","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1614,520],"id":"07c10e56-199a-2204-d992-890c2a8627c1","name":"Note: Merge Routed Work"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Stamp Processing Time\n\nStamps `processedAt` with the current time for auditing.\n\nNext: Align Field Names","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2586,520],"id":"fa60c588-a9c0-8453-a7c2-67628ceebada","name":"Note: Stamp Processing Time"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Align Field Names\n\nNormalizes field names so every source feeds the same downstream schema.\n\nNext: Cap Batch Volume","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2910,520],"id":"f8298b98-dc70-be9f-fcd1-cc3821c18ce3","name":"Note: Align Field Names"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Cap Batch Volume\n\nCaps the stream at 100 items to protect downstream quotas.","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3234,520],"id":"91138b2d-2bd4-5702-fe93-05c935816b88","name":"Note: Cap Batch Volume"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Approve requests with Discord and Google Drive hands-free\n\n**Pattern:** Approval Workflow · **Level:** Foundation · **Trigger:** Form\n\n## What it does\nApprove requests with Discord and Google Drive hands-free. It starts from a hosted form submission.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual standups is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nNew Task Form Submission → Route by Work Type → Process 'auto-approve' → Google Sheets → Merge Routed Work → Stamp Processing Time → Align Field Names → Cap Batch Volume\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to approval workflow without manual effort\n- Anyone automating standups in software development\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Improves response time\n- Saves hours of manual work each week\n- Has retries and error handling built in\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: Discord webhook URL; Google OAuth2 / service account.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"e7863067-1dc8-0a74-efcc-0e77b89d684e","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your standups process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-290],"id":"fd8c9c99-e54e-6c34-543c-5a521d6f0e94","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"New Task Form Submission":{"main":[[{"node":"Route by Work Type","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Route by Work Type":{"main":[[{"node":"Process 'auto-approve' → Google Sheets","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Fast-Track 'needs-review' + Alert","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Hold Unknown Types (DLQ)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Process 'auto-approve' → Google Sheets":{"main":[[{"node":"Merge Routed Work","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Fast-Track 'needs-review' + Alert":{"main":[[{"node":"Merge Routed Work","type":"main","index":1}]]},"Hold Unknown Types (DLQ)":{"main":[[{"node":"Merge Routed Work","type":"main","index":2}]]},"Merge Routed Work":{"main":[[{"node":"Stamp Processing Time","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Stamp Processing Time":{"main":[[{"node":"Align Field Names","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Align Field Names":{"main":[[{"node":"Cap Batch Volume","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"d21bf4e3-0958-4087-ba10-fd3877bb2f82","id":"FDX08460"}